title: Film-Noir | Not Wanted (1949) Sally Forrest, Keefe Brasselle, Leo Penn | an Ida Lupino Film

sources.title: Film-Noir | Not Wanted (1949) Sally Forrest, Keefe Brasselle, Leo Penn | an Ida Lupino Film
sources.description:
After a beautiful but unsophisticated girl is seduced by a worldly piano player and gives up her out-of-wedlock baby, her guilt compels her to kidnap another child.


Original title: Not Wanted (1949) AKA: Shame / Unwed Mother / Streets of Sin 
This movie is available with subtitles in many languages. 

Watch the HD Colorized version: https://youtu.be/DD5_py-PtC8
